      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle exemplifies a standard of care that ensures both longevity and consistent performance. Meticulously maintained and showing clear pride of ownership, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This offering represents a sophisticated choice for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of prestige and proven reliability. We invite you to experience the caliber of this well-preserved machine firsthand.",
      "price": 36500.0,
