      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a full suspension refresh utilizing polyurethane bushings to maintain structural rigidity. Maintenance is up to date, including a comprehensive double-VANOS system overhaul and recent valve clearance adjustments. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a direct, analog connection to the road that modern grand tourers lack.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
